Methodology
To
find
the
best
credit
cards
for
balance
transfers
we
looked
across
the
spectrum
of
cards
with
0%
APR
offers
on
shifting
debt.
Then,
we
selected
the
best
cards
for
individual
categories
such
as
lack
of
penalty
fees,
length
of
the
promotional
period
and
no
cost
to
carry
the
card.
The
best
cards
were
chosen
based
on
what
made
them
stand
out
from
the
pack.
That
said,
what
is
best
for
the
majority
of
people
might
not
be
right
for
you.
Do
your
research
before
deciding
which
cards
will
best
help
you
achieve
your
balance
transfer
goals.
